y creating a repeat sale  the customer wins with a quality vehicle at a payment that is affordable with respect to their income nicholas wins by recognizing a reasonable profit versus the associated risk over the term of the contract why use nicholas financial     experience each of our branch managers loan officers have years of experience in automobile indirect and direct lending to customerslocation all of our branch offices are within a short drive from the dealers that they serve responsiveness we take pride in calling back our dealers within hours of receipt of the sales application positive purchasing our buyers work hard for you by looking for ways to put a deal together  we commit to you a high percentage of approvals predictability  reliability when we set up a relationship to arrange to aquire your installment sales contracts we tell you what you can expect our call to be  in this manner we develop apredictable and reliable relationship with you funding we are backed by one of the largest banks in the united states bankamerica with a revolving line of credit  we are a publically traded corporation with extensive capital resources  if we agree to fund a dealer we do it accuracy our computer systems and software were designed by our own software subsidiary nicholas data services inc and represent millions of dollars in research and development   because of this we are able to provide you with flexible terms payment schedules and most importantly accurate rate information availability we are available monday through friday from am to pm forms     you can download and print the following forms from this website  the adobe pdf plugin is required click here for adobe acrobat readerplugin software automatic payment authorization automobile dealer retail purchase agreement corporate resolution and signature card dealer ach funding authorization dealer cash out check list credit statement guarantee of title reference sheet assignment form cosigner form discount di